column5: We have a open spot for quinte opener,$85 covers you for the whole weekend, just bring your gear, food beer, needing a non-boater to fish with another member, must split gas with the boater and purchase a derby ticket, cottage is at Perfect Vue just inside hay bay, heated!(Previous person had to back out due to purchasing a boat from the states and the time frame may not work for him!)Must be paid to me up front to hold spot, as accomedations are all paid up! Thanks for looking Wayne!
